# Hardware Request & Installation — Full Review & Fix Plan

## Executive Summary

Deep audit 18 file (3895 LOC). Ditemukan **14 bug/issue** di hardware request + hardware installation pages. 2 critical issue sesuai user request (installation schedule broken, searchbar disconnected) + 12 issue lain yg impact UX/logic.

