## Bug & Issue Inventory

### 🔴 P0 — CRITICAL (User-reported)

#### BUG-1: Installation Schedule Modal — `scheduledDate` Timezone Bug
**File:** [InstallationScheduleModal.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/features/request-center/components/InstallationScheduleModal.tsx)  
**Root Cause:** Backend `getMonthlyAvailability()` di [installation-schedule.service.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/backend/src/modules/ticketing/services/installation-schedule.service.ts) mutasi `startDate` saat loop:
```javascript
// BUG: d.setDate(d.getDate() + 1) MUTASI startDate (same reference)
for (let d = new Date(startDate); d <= endDate; d.setDate(d.getDate() + 1)) {
    const dateStr = d.toISOString().split('T')[0];
```
`d.toISOString()` return UTC → timezone mismatch dengan Postgres `date` column. Juga `scheduledDate` column type `date` tapi query pakai `Between(startOfDay, endOfDay)` dengan timestamp — bisa miss data.

**Juga:** Jika DB belum ada data schedule sama sekali, `getAvailableSlots()` tetap return slot available, tapi di frontend `getDayAvailability()` return `null` untuk hari yg tidak ada di response → hari tampil tanpa dot → user bingung.

#### BUG-2: Hardware Request Page Searchbar — Client-Side Only, Not Connected to Backend/GlobalSearch
**File:** [HardwareRequestPage.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/features/request-center/pages/HardwareRequestPage.tsx#L42-L62)  
**Root Cause:** Searchbar hanya filter `filteredRequests` via client-side string match:
```javascript
const filteredRequests = requests.filter(req => {
    const matchesSearch = (req.title?.toLowerCase() || req.budgetCategory?.toLowerCase() || '').includes(debouncedSearchTerm.toLowerCase());
    return matchesSearch;
});
```
**Problems:**
1. `debouncedSearchTerm` TIDAK dikirim ke `useIctBudgetRequests()` → backend returns semua data tanpa search
2. Pattern `req.title?.toLowerCase() || req.budgetCategory?.toLowerCase()` hanya match satu field (jika title truthy, category diabaikan)
3. Pagination + client-side filter = hanya search page pertama
4. Tidak terhubung ke GlobalSearch (`useSearch` hook pakai `/search` endpoint terpisah)

