### 🟡 P1 — MAJOR (Workflow/Logic Bugs)

#### BUG-3: Backend `findAll` — `search` parameter TIDAK DI-SUPPORT
**File:** [ict-budget.controller.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/backend/src/modules/ict-budget/ict-budget.controller.ts#L35-L61)  
Controller & service `findAll()` hanya accept `siteId`, `status`, `page`, `limit`. Tidak ada `search` parameter.

#### BUG-4: `getMonthlyAvailability` — Date Loop Mutation
**File:** [installation-schedule.service.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/backend/src/modules/ticketing/services/installation-schedule.service.ts)  
`for (let d = new Date(startDate)...)` mutasi `startDate` karena `setDate()` modifies in-place. Loop bisa skip hari atau infinite loop.

#### BUG-5: Slot Data Shape Mismatch Frontend↔Backend
**Frontend** `InstallationScheduleModal` expect:
```ts
slots: { time: string; available: boolean; capacity: number; booked: number }[]
```
**Backend** `getMonthlyAvailability` returns per-day `slots` tapi nested inside daily result. Frontend `getDayAvailability()` match by `a.date === dateStr` → **correct shape**. Tapi jika MongoDB empty, all days return `available: true` padahal no slot data → misleading availability display.

#### BUG-6: InstallationDetailPage — Wrong Route for ICT Budget Link
**File:** [InstallationDetailPage.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/pages/HardwareInstallation/InstallationDetailPage.tsx#L166)
```tsx
navigate(`/ict-budget/${detail.ictBudgetRequest?.id}`)
```
Tapi route yg benar adalah `/hardware-requests/${id}`. Route `/ict-budget/` TIDAK EXIST di router.

#### BUG-7: InstallationDetailPage — `detail.ictBudgetRequest.title` field TIDAK return dari backend
**File:** Backend `findOneInstallation()` hanya select `['id', 'realizationStatus']` dari ictBudgetRequest. Field `title` tidak di-select sehingga selalu undefined.

#### BUG-8: InstallationDetailPage — Schedule Status Display Wrong Values
**File:** [InstallationDetailPage.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/pages/HardwareInstallation/InstallationDetailPage.tsx#L213-L219)
Cek `detail.schedule.status === 'ARRIVED'` dan `'REALIZED'` tapi ScheduleStatus enum hanya: `PENDING`, `APPROVED`, `RESCHEDULED`, `COMPLETED`, `CANCELLED`. Tidak ada `ARRIVED` atau `REALIZED`.

#### BUG-9: `useHardwareStats` — Fetch ALL 1000 tickets for stats computation
**File:** [useHardwareInstallation.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/hooks/useHardwareInstallation.ts#L27-L34)
`useAllHardwareTickets` fetch limit 1000 tiap kali. Ini wasteful dan bisa slow. Stats should come from backend aggregation.

