#### BUG-10: HardwareRequestPage — Tab Count Inaccurate
**File:** [HardwareRequestPage.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/features/request-center/pages/HardwareRequestPage.tsx#L123-L125)
