#### BUG-13: HardwareRequestPage — Pagination resets tapi status filter tidak reset search
Saat ganti tab, `setPage(1)` tapi `searchTerm` tidak di-clear. User bisa stuck di "no results" tanpa sadar searchbar punya value.

#### BUG-14: InstallationTab → handleRowClick navigates tanpa role-based path
**File:** [InstallationTab.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/frontend/src/features/request-center/components/InstallationTab.tsx#L58-L64)
Navigasi langsung ke `/hardware-requests/${id}?highlight=installation` tanpa prefix `/client` atau `/manager`. Works for agent tapi broken untuk user/manager role karena mereka punya prefix di route.

